        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "## Spark Troubleshooting\n\n**Common Issues:**\n\n1. **Master Unreachable**: Check master pod logs\n2. **Worker Not Connecting**: Verify network connectivity between pods\n3. **Job Failing**: Check executor memory settings\n4. **Slow Performance**: Monitor memory usage - may need tuning\n\n**Useful Commands:**\n```bash\n# View Spark master logs\nkubectl logs -n ldp -l app=spark-master\n\n# View worker logs\nkubectl logs -n ldp -l app=spark-worker\n\n# Access Spark UI\nmake spark-forward\n# Then open http://localhost:8080\n\n# Submit a test job\nkubectl exec -n ldp spark-master-0 -- \\\n  spark-submit --master spark://spark-master:7077 \\\n  /opt/spark/examples/src/main/python/pi.py 10\n```\n\n**Resource Tuning:**\n- Executor memory: `spark.executor.memory`\n- Driver memory: `spark.driver.memory`\n- Cores per executor: `spark.executor.cores`",
